data.description: Adorable all brick ranch in Donelson's Stanford Estates neighborhood!  This light-filled home features hardwood floors, a formal living room, plus a den with a fireplace and bay window! The bathroom has been nicely updated with white tile.  There is a screened/glassed-in porch that opens off the dining area, that is perfect for relaxing!  The back of the home has a large deck overlooking the spacious yard.  2 car- carport with extra storage.  Close to shopping, restaurants, the new Ravenwood Park, and Percy Priest Lake.  No HOA.
